{"tid":1307263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（想組團）有冇人有興趣追擊民生政策","createTime":"2019-07-11T13:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T05:06:23.000Z","uid":73912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea9996e460be78abeb3d893cd68a44f5d14f5ca4","tid":1307263,"uid":73912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"見到而家有部份人已經準備緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有好多人都見到社區好多問題<br />\n<br />\n或者政策上面有問題！越來越多人關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以睇吓有冇人有興趣一齊研究某啲課題<br />\n<br />\n瘋狂宣傳 某啲人嘅（失職）或者某啲好離譜嘅問題<br />\n一齊睇下區議會報告一齊搵吓資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我本身自己做緊 星期六或者星期日都會抽啲時間<br />\n<br />\n睇下報告睇吓議員講咗啲咩 睇吓點樣出賣市民<br />\n<br />\n所以如果多啲人一齊做嘅話 力量就可以更加大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f6f165aae0daa90fd0722577976d0ee8510045","tid":1307263,"uid":73912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1729bdb87daa08353369fefd4669b0c1d6d734","tid":1307263,"uid":73912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd91e55450a91ca8762a86da108b4710857a62e9","tid":1307263,"uid":73912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7027564e6cb754fc08279b07668cfa2a0bbcd97","tid":1307263,"uid":73912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac46cda64d3464254c20679cfd4e98c377a25877","tid":1307263,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:38